content:
Analyze this project brief: 'I want a child story with a magical puppet
add some moral to the story and make some adventure. 
The story is very short, less than 1000 words'.
Generate the required team structure.
Respond ONLY with a JSON matching this exact structure. Use short, unique words for 'team_name' and 'task_name' (e.g., 'Backend', 'UI', 'Database'):
{
  "managers": [
    {
      "team_name": "ShortTeamName",
      "role": "Detailed description of their role",
      "employees": [
        {"task_name": "ShortTaskName", "role": "Their specific role"}
      ]
    }
  ]
}

{
  "managers": [
    {
      "team_name": "Fable",
      "role": "Orchestrates narrative construction, adventure pacing, magical integration, moral embedding, and strict word-count enforcement.",
      "employees": [
        {"task_name": "Arc", "role": "Maps adventure sequence and plot progression"},
        {"task_name": "Charm", "role": "Develops magical puppet mechanics and presence"},
        {"task_name": "Lesson", "role": "Weaves ethical theme into story resolution"},
        {"task_name": "Prune", "role": "Trims and polishes text to guarantee sub-1000-word limit"}
      ]
    }
  ]
}
